org.sakaiproject.entity.api

Interface EntityTransferrer

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    RWikiObjectService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AssessmentEntityProducer, BaseAnnouncementService, BaseAssignmentService, BaseCalendarService, BaseContentService, BasicNewsService, ChatEntityProducer, DbAnnouncementService, DbAssignmentService, DbCalendarService, DbContentService, DiscussionForumServiceImpl, GlossaryEntityProducer, GradebookEntityProducer, LessonBuilderEntityProducer, LinkToolEntityProducer, MatrixContentEntityProducer, MetaobjContentEntityProducer, MetaobjEntityProducer, PollListManagerImpl, PresentationContentEntityProducer, ReportDefEntityProducer, RWikiObjectServiceImpl, SyllabusServiceImpl, WebServiceImpl, WizardEntityProducer

    public interface EntityTransferrer

    Services which implement EntityTransferrer declare themselves as willing and able to transfer/copy their entities from one context to another.
